Define a class to represent a bank account. Include the following members:

Data members
(a) Name of the depositor
(b) Account number
(c) Type of account
(d) Balance amount in the account

Member functions
(a) To assign initial values
(b) To deposit an amount
(c) To withdraw an amount after checking the balance
(d) To display name and balance

Write a main program to test the program.


(i)  Implement the program to Handle a Single customer
(ii) Extend the program to handle 3 customers
(iii)Extend the program to implement Array of Objects(10 customers)
(iv) Make the program run until user want to exit.
